data.description: A must see! 2-bed, 2.5-bath townhome located in a quiet, beautiful community in West Palm Beach. Open-concept living, two spacious ensuite bedrooms, private patio, community pool. Newly painted walls, ceiling fans, toilets, tub, shower enclosure and light fixtures. Upgraded tile throughout. New roof and fence enclosure. Community offers clubhouse, pool, and fitness gym. Conveniently located close to I-95, schools, shopping, dining, Palm Beach Outlets and PBIA.
